## Skills changes proposed

This is the bridge from "what happened" to "what changes." If this section is
empty and the project had any failures, you're not looking hard enough.

### New skills
- **`<category>/<name>`** — <one-sentence why; reference specific incident>

### Modify existing
- **`<skill-name>`** — <what to sharpen or add; reference specific incident>

### Delete
- **`<skill-name>`** — <why it didn't pull its weight in this project>

---

## Time spent

Rough numbers — don't over-engineer the tracking.

- **Total dev hours**: <number>
- **Hours saved by skills** (estimate): <number>
- **Hours spent on skill ceremony** (estimate): <number>
- **Net**: <saved - ceremony>

If ceremony > saved consistently across projects, the package is too heavy.
If saved >> ceremony, you might be under-applying skills.

---

