## Refinement ritual completed?

- [ ] Bug archaeology done (30 min)
- [ ] Friction audit done (30 min)
- [ ] Skill files updated and committed
- [ ] CHANGELOG.md updated with version bump
- [ ] VERSION file bumped
- [ ] Validated changes against 3 real bugs from this project

If any box is unchecked, the retrospective isn't done.
